e least amount of budget needed to achieve the output target.This paper was accepted by David Simchi-Levi, operations management.Funding: This work was partially supported by the National Natural Science Foundation of China [Grants 71471062, 72032001 and 71972071] and the Shanghai Sailing Program [Grant 22YF1451000].Supplemental Material: The online appendix is available at https://doi.org/10.1287/mnsc.2023.4749.
