T1  - The Influence of Short Selling on Negative Press Coverage of Firms
AU  - Bushman, Robert
AU  - Pinto, Jedson
Y1  - 2023/05/05
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4783
